name: David Key Fresno DJ Specialist
overview:
At the age of 24, David Key Fresno is becoming the name in DJ services.

Key Party Productions is your #1 source for Party Entertainment in the area, offering DJ/MCs, Wedding Bands, Dancers, Entertainment of all types, Lighting and more. We cover the entire Central Valley including: Fresno, Madera, Tulare and Bakersfield.

Party Like a Rock Star

Founded in 2008, David Key’s Party Time Productions has developed the best group of local DJ / Master of Ceremonies you can trust to make your event a blast! We pride ourselves on our professionalism and dependability.

We have been doing one thing extremely well – entertaining your guests. Let our Disc Jockey’s reputation for success make your event unforgettable, fabulous and fun!

We set the tone for your celebration. We are not only good with music – we are good with you and your guests. We have the experience you can count on to make your party a great success.

Our DJs are the best in the business and can handle groups from 50 to 5,000. They are trained to read the crowd and respond with a smooth mix of dance favorites that keep the dance floor packed!
